data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home on 1.82 acres in amazing Palo Cedro. 2 car attached garage PLUS 3 car detached garage/SHOP with 1/2 bath in shop. Newer roof just 3 years ago, newer exterior paint with freshly cleared landscape. New interior flooring with nice open floor plan. New Solar (leased). Bring your toys and invite all your company to this wonderful home ready for all kinds of entertainment.
